PN,44901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772216417
OL,3,CYouTube broadcast 'pre-recorded' on
OL,4,Cnight of Natalie killing
OL,6,FThe trial of a man accused of
OL,7,Fmurdering Natalie McNally, who was 15
OL,8,Fweeks pregnant when she was strangled,
OL,9,Fstabbed and beaten, has been told by a
OL,10,FPSNI cybercrime expert the YouTube
OL,11,Fvideo of Stephen McCullagh was 'pre
OL,12,Frecorded' and not live.
OL,14,FThe online 'live' broadcast was six
OL,15,Fhours long and went out on the social
OL,16,Fmedia video-sharing platform on Sunday
OL,17,F18th of December 2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772216417
OL,3,CYouTube broadcast 'pre-recorded' on
OL,4,Cnight of Natalie killing
OL,6,FThe prosecution case is that the
OL,7,Fgaming video was a "cover story" for
OL,8,FMcCullagh and the defendant 'peddled a
OL,9,Ffalse alibi' to get away with
OL,10,Fmurdering the 32-year-old.
OL,12,FSomething the 36-year-old from
OL,13,FWoodland Gardens in Lisburn denies.
OL,15,FThe detective constable, who is a
OL,16,Fdigital forensic analyst with the
OL,17,FPSNI, told the jury after extensively
OL,18,Fexamining the footage on the device
OL,19,F"the broadcast was pre-recorded and
OL,20,Flater streamed as a live event".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772216417
OL,3,CYouTube broadcast 'pre-recorded' on
OL,4,Cnight of Natalie killing
OL,6,FThe expert explained content creators
OL,7,Fdo live streaming encouraging
OL,8,Finteraction with the audience - he
OL,9,Fagreed it's for people to send
OL,10,Fmessages into the broadcast.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, part of the footage was
OL,13,Fshown to the jury and during it
OL,14,FMcCullagh referred to being live a
OL,15,Fnumber of times and explained how the
OL,16,Flive chat wasn't working because of
OL,17,Fthe internet so the audience could not
OL,18,Fmessage him.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772216417
OL,3,CYouTube broadcast 'pre-recorded' on
OL,4,Cnight of Natalie killing
OL,6,FThe expert also told the court that
OL,7,Fafter examining the online content
OL,8,Fthere was no user interaction
OL,9,Fwhatsoever during McCullagh's stream,
OL,10,Funlike you would find if it was
OL,11,Fbroadcast live.
OL,13,FThe jury heard the video was created
OL,14,Fon the 14th of December and the
OL,15,Frecording finished and was saved in
OL,16,Fthe early hours of the 15th December.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
