PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772216417
OL,3,CYouTube broadcast 'pre-recorded' on
OL,4,Cnight of Natalie killing
OL,6,FThe video was then streamed on 18th of
OL,7,FDecember - the day Natalie McNally was
OL,8,Fmurdered - before being deleted at six
OL,9,Fminutes past midnight on 19th of
OL,10,FDecember.
OL,12,FThe trial has already heard that when
OL,13,FStephen McCullagh was arrested in
OL,14,FFebruary 2023 and challenged about the
OL,15,FYouTube stream in a prepared statement
OL,16,Fhe admitted to police it was pre-
OL,17,Frecorded and on the night Natalie was
OL,18,Fkilled he had been drinking and fell
OL,19,Fasleep.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
